ViewObject.Name: ProjectView
ViewObject.SQLQuery: SELECT Project.ID, Project.CODE, Project.CODE PIX_REFERENCE, Project.NAME, Project.DESCRIPTION, Project.CATEGORY_CODE, Project.PHASE_CODE, Project.SYNC_DATE, Project.CREATE_DATE, Project.UPDATE_DATE, Project.PROGRAM_ID, Project.IS_SYNCING, Project.IS_LEAD, Project.SOURCE_CODE, Project.SUBSTANCE_TYPE_CODE, Project.TERMINATION_CODE, Project.IS_HPR, Project.ABBREVIATION, Project.IS_COLLABORATION, Project.IS_PIP, Project.IS_PORTFOLIO, Project.PRIORITY_CODE, Project.REVIEW_DATE, Project.STATE_CODE, Project.URL_DEVELOPMENT_PLAN, Project.URL_PRODUCT_PROFILE, Project.SHAREDOC_ID, nvl2(Project.SHAREDOC_ID,(select value from configuration where code='SHAREDOC')||Project.SHAREDOC_ID,null) as URL_SHAREDOC, Project.TERMINATION_REASON AS TERMINATION_REASON1, ProjectCategory.NAME AS NAME1, ProjectCategory.CODE AS CODE1, SubstanceType.NAME AS NAME2, SubstanceType.CODE AS CODE2, ProjectSource.NAME AS NAME3, ProjectSource.CODE AS CODE3, Phase.NAME AS NAME4, Phase.CODE AS CODE4, TerminationReason.NAME AS NAME7, TerminationReason.CODE AS CODE7, ProjectState.NAME AS NAME8, ProjectState.CODE AS CODE8, Priority.NAME AS NAME9, Priority.CODE AS CODE9, ProjectArea.NAME AS NAME10, ProjectArea.CODE AS CODE10, Project.AREA_CODE, Project.TERMINATION_DATE, Project.DEVELOPMENT_PHASE_CODE, DevelopmentPhase.NAME AS NAME12, DevelopmentPhase.CODE AS CODE12, Bay.NAME AS NAME13, Bay.CODE AS CODE13, Project.bay_code, Sbe.NAME AS NAME14, Sbe.CODE AS CODE14, Project.sbe_code, Project.enpv, Project.npv, Project.peak_sales, Project.details_criteria, Project.details_mesh, Project.details_indication, Project.details_product, Project.details_goal, Project.details_action, Project.details_asia, Project.details_competition, Project.details_patent, Project.details_sales, Project.details_pmo, Project.details_partner, Project.details_comment, Project.is_regional, Project.is_orphan_drug, Project.is_direct_phase3, Project.is_combined_phase2, Project.is_pdco_positive, Project.is_waiver, Project.pip_activities, Project.details_progress, Project.ta_code, Ta.NAME AS NAME15, Ta.CODE AS CODE15, Project.tc_code, Tc.NAME AS NAME17, Tc.CODE AS CODE17, Project.to_code, Tor.NAME AS NAME18, Tor.CODE AS CODE18, Gbu.NAME AS NAME16, Gbu.CODE AS CODE16, Project.pip_date, Project.pdco_date, Project.pidt_release_date, Project.progress_date, Project.planning_code PLANNING_CODE, Project.ipowner_code, mgr.code main_group_code, mgr.name main_group_name, tgr.code top_group_code, tgr.name top_group_name, TimeLineWTypes.id as timeline_raw_id, Project.ACCOUNTING_STATUS, Project.SUCCESSOR_PROJECT_ID, Project.PLANNING_ENABLED, Project.CURRENT_COMMENT, Project.COMMENT_PREVIOUS_FC, Project.CONTROLLING_PROJECT_TYPE, ProjectArea.IS_PIDT, Project.QPLAN_RELEASE_DATE, Project.is_active, Combi.COMBINATION_CODE, Combi.COMBINATION_NAME, Project.GBU_Code, Project.pidt_bu_code, pidt_bu.name pidt_bu_name, Project.PROPOSED_SBE_CODE, Project.import_program_code IMPORT_PROGRAM_CODE, Project.import_program_name IMPORT_PROGRAM_NAME, Project.predecessor_project_id PREDECESSOR_PROJECT_ID, Project.d3transition_project_id D3TRANSITION_PROJECT_ID, Project.succ_project_id SUCC_PROJECT_ID, Project.CATEGORY_CODE subgroup_code, Project.is_typify_excluded IS_TYPIFY_EXCLUDED, case when Project.program_id='RBIN' then 'deleted' when Project.is_active=1 then 'active' else 'inactive' end SEARCH_STATUS, case when Project.program_id='RBIN' then 'deleted' when Project.is_active=1 then 'active' else 'inactive' end SEARCH_STATUS2, Project.CODE SEARCH_CODE, Project.NAME||','||Project.previous_names SEACH_NAME, Project.NAME||','||Project.previous_names SEACH_NAME_MNT, Project.CODE SEARCH_CODE_MNT, (select 1 from timeline tm where tm.project_id=project.id and tm.type_code='CUR') as IS_CURRENT_PLAN, (select 1 from timeline tm where tm.project_id=project.id and tm.type_code='RAW') as IS_RAW_PLAN, 0 constant_false, Project.lo_review_meeting_date, Project.lo_review_result_code, Project.D2_COMPOUND, Project.TRG, Project.TARGET_GENE_CODE, Project.ER, Project.GENERAL_PROJECT_FRAME, Project.D1_DECISION_DATE, Project.D1_DECISION_DATE as D1_DECISION_DATE_FLT_TO, Project.LSA_DATE, Project.START_HTS_DATE, milestone_poc.poc_date poc_milestone_date, Project.phase_estimated_code, Project.d2_planned_date, Project.d2_achieved_date, Project.ptr_for_d2_code, Project.previous_names, Project.d3transition_project_id D3TRANSITION_PROJECT_ID_OLD, ProjectArea.is_running_import, Project.IS_DEVICE_PROJECT, Project.project_device_type_code, Project.bpi_no, Project.details_modality, Project.REGULATORY_CODE, Project.REGULATORY_OTHER, Project.DEVICE_PHASE_CODE, Project.DETAILS_OBJECTIVE, Project.DETAILS_RATIONALE, Project.DETAILS_RISKS , Project.DETAILS_INTENDED_USE, Project.DETAILS_EXECUTIVE_SUMMARY , Project.DETAILS_SCOPE, Project.DETAILS_HIGHLIGHTS , Project.DETAILS_BENEFITS , Project.DETAILS_ACTIVITIES_EVENTS , Project.DETAILS_BUDGET , Project.DETAILS_BUDGET_STATUS, Project.DETAILS_SAMD_STATUS, Project.IS_EXTERNAL_PORTFOLIO FROM PROJECT Project left join prj_cost_probabilities_vw cost_prob ON cost_prob.project_id = Project.ID left join PROJECT_CATEGORY ProjectCategory on Project.CATEGORY_CODE = ProjectCategory.CODE and ProjectCategory.is_active=1 left join SUBSTANCE_TYPE SubstanceType on Project.SUBSTANCE_TYPE_CODE = SubstanceType.CODE left join PROJECT_SOURCE ProjectSource on Project.SOURCE_CODE = ProjectSource.CODE left join PHASE Phase on Project.PHASE_CODE = Phase.CODE left join TERMINATION_REASON TerminationReason on Project.TERMINATION_CODE = TerminationReason.CODE left join PROJECT_STATE ProjectState on Project.STATE_CODE = ProjectState.CODE left join PRIORITY Priority on Project.PRIORITY_CODE = Priority.CODE left join PROJECT_AREA ProjectArea on Project.AREA_CODE = ProjectArea.CODE left join DEVELOPMENT_PHASE DevelopmentPhase on Project.DEVELOPMENT_PHASE_CODE = DevelopmentPhase.CODE left join BAY_NUMBER Bay on Project.BAY_CODE = Bay.CODE left join STRATEGIC_BUSINESS_ENTITY Sbe on Project.SBE_CODE = Sbe.CODE left join THERAPEUTIC_AREA Ta on Project.TA_CODE = Ta.CODE left join GLOBAL_BUSINESS_UNIT Gbu on Project.GBU_CODE = Gbu.CODE left join TARGET_CLASS Tc on Project.TC_CODE = Tc.CODE left join TARGET_ORIGIN Tor on Project.TO_CODE = Tor.CODE left join combination_vw Combi on Project.ID = Combi.PROJECT_ID left join maingroup mgr on mgr.code=ProjectCategory.maingroup_code and mgr.is_active=1 left join topgroup tgr on tgr.code=mgr.topgroup_code and tgr.is_active=1 left join global_business_unit pidt_bu on Project.pidt_bu_code = pidt_bu.code left join ( select Timeline.id, Timeline.Project_ID from TIMELINE Timeline join TIMELINE_TYPE TimelineType on TimelineType.CODE = Timeline.TYPE_CODE where Timeline.type_code = 'RAW' ) TimeLineWTypes on TimeLineWTypes.project_id = Project.ID left join (select project_id, min(milestone_date) poc_date from milestone_vw where milestone_code='PoC' and timeline_type_code='CUR' group by project_id) milestone_poc on milestone_poc.project_id=project.id WHERE (Project.area_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:AllowedProjectTypes))) or Project.area_code in (select column_value from table(stringlist_to_table(:AllowedAssignedProjectTypes))) and exists(select * from user_role where UPPER(user_id)=UPPER(:UserNameVar) and program_id=project.program_id) or :RoleTypify='true' and Project.area_code is null) and nvl(:SearchProjectName,1)=nvl(:SearchProjectName,1) and nvl(:SearchProjectNameMnt,1)=nvl(:SearchProjectNameMnt,1) and nvl(:SearchProjectCode,1)=nvl(:SearchProjectCode,1) and nvl(:SearchProjectCodeMnt,1)=nvl(:SearchProjectCodeMnt,1) and nvl(:SearchIsHpr,1)=nvl(:SearchIsHpr,1) and nvl(:SearchIsPortfolio,1)=nvl(:SearchIsPortfolio,1) and nvl(:SearchSbeCode,1)=nvl(:SearchSbeCode,1) and nvl(:SearchAreaCode,1)=nvl(:SearchAreaCode,1) and nvl(:SearchBUCodeVar,1)=nvl(:SearchBUCodeVar,1) and nvl(:SearchStatusVar,1)=nvl(:SearchStatusVar,1) and nvl(:SearchStatusMnt,1)=nvl(:SearchStatusMnt,1) and nvl(:CurrentLeTagIdVar,1)=nvl(:CurrentLeTagIdVar,1) and nvl(:CurrentLtcTagIdVar,1)=nvl(:CurrentLtcTagIdVar,1) and nvl(:SearchPocDateFromVar,1)=nvl(:SearchPocDateFromVar,1) and nvl(:SearchPocDateToVar,1)=nvl(:SearchPocDateToVar,1) and nvl(:SearchDevelopmentPhaseCodeVar,1)=nvl(:SearchDevelopmentPhaseCodeVar,1) and nvl(:SearchProjectIsActive,1)=nvl(:SearchProjectIsActive,1) and nvl(:SearchProjectBayCodeVar,1)=nvl(:SearchProjectBayCodeVar,1) and nvl(:SearchProjectTaCodeVar,1)=nvl(:SearchProjectTaCodeVar,1) and nvl(:SearchProjectBayCodeMnt,1)=nvl(:SearchProjectBayCodeMnt,1) and nvl(:SearchStudyCodeVar,1)=nvl(:SearchStudyCodeVar,1) order by upper(name)

CompOper.Name: Id_Oper
CompOper.TransientExpression: return " IN (select sd.project_id from study_data_vw sd where sd.timeline_type_code in ('CUR','RAW') and instr(lower(sd.study_id),lower(:SearchStudyCodeVar))>0) or :SearchStudyCodeVar is null"
